    <li>Lee, K., & Garcia, L. (2021). *Green Tech in Cloud Computing*. FutureDigital.</li>
    <li>Taylor, R. (2023). *Ethical Digital Infrastructure*. OpenTech Books.</li>
  </ul>
</section>

